description:
For testing an app and mobile site I have developed I need a Virtualbox Android virtual machine.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am not familiar with Android and it is taking a lot of time to figure out exactly how to create the virtual machine.&nbsp;&nbsp;I need a walkthrough.
One of the issues I am running into is that my app checks if the user is using a smartphone.&nbsp;&nbsp;In previous iterations of the Android virtualbox VM that I attempted to load to test my app, my app was rejecting the VM because it was stating that it is not a smartphone.&nbsp;&nbsp;
In order to be usable for full testing of my app, the solution you provide must appear to be an Android phone to apps and mobile sites which are visited through the VM.<b>Skills</b>:        Android,                     Android App Development
